WE BELIEVE THAT OUR MAJOR PROPERTIES ARE ADEQUATE FOR OUR PRESENT NEEDS AND, AS SUPPLEMENTED BY PLANNED IMPROVEMENTS AND CONSTRUCTION, EXPECT THEM TO REMAIN ADEQUATE FOR THE FORESEEABLE FUTURE.

