WE ALSO HOLD CERTAIN DERIVATIVE INSTRUMENTS, PRIMARILY FOREIGN CURRENCY FORWARD CONTRACTS, FOR RISK MANAGEMENT PURPOSES THAT ARE NOT RECEIVING HEDGE ACCOUNTING TREATMENT.

